<DATE>
<P>
January 10, 1994, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
