<DOCNO> LA011094-0024 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 002687 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 10, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 7; Column 2; Op-Ed Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
