<P>
GETTY GRANT PROGRAM DEADLINE IS FEB. 1 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Deadline for visual arts organizations' applications to the Getty Grant 
Program's multicultural summer internships is Feb. 1. 
</P>
<P>
 Museums and educational institutions located in Los Angeles County are invited 
to apply for up to three stipends of $3,000 each, to be paid to student interns 
over a 10-week period in the summer. 
</P>
<P>
 Organizations that are selected will choose their own interns. Undergraduate 
college students of African American, Asian, Latino, Native American and 
Pacific Islander descent who have completed at least one year of college and 
remain enrolled will be eligible for the internships. 
</P>
<P>
 For application instructions write: the Getty Grant Program, 401 Wilshire 
Blvd., Ste. 1000, Santa Monica, Calif. 90401, call (310) 393-4244 or telefax 
(310) 395-8642. 
</P>
