<DOCID> 002779 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 10, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
